collections.name: The Stone of Mars' Power: A New Beginning
collections.description:
Mars is the next frontier that humanity will eventually colonize. 
However, this journey is not just a trip; it is a completely new 
beginning. ‘The Stone of Mars' Power: A New Beginning’ NFT 
embodies this pioneering spirit and the significance of the challenge 
ahead.
This NFT is composed of three special stones—‘The Stone of 
Beginning,’ ‘The Stone of Purpose,’ and ‘The Stone of Success’—
each representing a stage in humanity's journey toward the unknown.
‘The Stone of Beginning’: Every journey starts with the first step. 
This stone symbolizes the decision to embrace a new challenge 
and the courage to take that first step.
‘The Stone of Purpose’: Along the way, there are times when we may 
feel lost. This stone represents the moment we refocus on our 
goal and find the strength to continue moving forward.
‘The Stone of Success’: After persistent effort and challenge, this 
stone marks the achievement of the goal. It is not just the end of 
the challenge, but the moment that opens.

collections.name: Tokyograff
collections.description: Tokyograff is a collection of NFTs that merges two seemingly opposing worlds: the tradition of Japanese art and the rebellious energy of urban graffiti. Each work is a visual journey that challenges convention, showcasing iconic figures such as geisha, samurai, dragons, and yokai spirits, but with a modern twist. Graffiti strokes, bursts of neon color, and sarcastic phrases invade spaces where calm and serenity should reign. With a blend of respect for the ancient and a cheeky interpretation of the present, this collection reflects the duality of our era: a world where tradition and modernity coexist and redefine each other. "Shin-Graffiti" is for those who believe that art should not only be contemplation, but also provocation and an expression of freedom.
